	<h1 class="title">南美第一站，小米的巴西办公室长这样</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/1329/small/1329.jpg?1418779602" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">胡莹 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-08-12 13:19:24 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/13397/medium/13397.jpg?1439351892" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


